name: Light Support Sports bralette
description: Sports bralette with light support suitable for low-intensity workouts and a fast-drying function designed to help keep you dry and cool while moving

name: Twill Cargo Pants
description: Fitted cargo pants in cotton-blend twill. Low waist, zip fly with button, and small patch pockets at top with flap and snap fastener.

name: Wide jersey dress
description: Long, wide dress in softly draping jersey with a V-neck at the front and narrow shoulder straps that are twisted and tie at the partially open back. Straight cut hem.

name: Collared Rib-knit Dress
description: Fitted, knee-length dress in rib-knit fabric with wool content. Collar, buttons at top, and long sleeves. Slit at cuffs and at sides of hem.

name: Flounced Crêped Wrap Dress
description: Short dress in softly draped, woven, crêped viscose fabric.

name: V-neck Sweater
description: Relaxed-fit sweater in a soft, fine-knit viscose blend. V-neck, dropped shoulders, and long sleeves.

name: High Waist twill trousers
description: Long, 5-pocket trousers in slightly stretchy cotton twill that will flatter any figure.

name: Textured-weave Jacket
description: Double-breasted jacket in woven, textured fabric. Pointed lapels, buttons at front, discreet welt front pockets, and decorative buttons at cuffs.

name: Cotton-blend Flounced Blouse
description: Short blouse in a woven cotton blend. Wide flounces at neckline and at front. Low-cut neckline, open front with narrow ties, and long sleeves with drawstring and flared cuffs. Unlined.

name: Rib-knit Dress
description: Fitted, calf-length dress in a rib knit. Sweetheart neckline, long sleeves, and a straight-cut hem.
